title: Celebrity Gossip Part 1 - Ethan Hawke Watched A Co-Star Die
description: At the age of 45, Ryan Reynolds is very thankful that The American Cancer Society now recommends getting a colonoscopy at 45 instead of 50, and Ethan Hawke watched a co-star die. Not acting die… life leaving his body die. It’s a crazy story.
